resources.string: I have never been as good as I’ve wanted to be to you. Yet your love for me makes me want to go on. I love you, darling
Your kindness and compassion fill me with awe. Love, thank you for being all that I could ask for in a woman and so much more
Were you really born on this day? Or did you just fly down from heaven as the beautiful angel you are?
It’s your birthday, but I’m the one who should be celebrating the most. My favorite person in the world was born on this day
Happy Birthday Dear Davin From Family and Friends
